===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
{{en-noun|informations|-}} (Short form: [[info]])

# A collection of related data.
# Knowledge about a topic.
# [[Data]] that have been processed into a [[format]] that is understandable by its intended audience.
# A service provided by [[telephone]] which provides listed telephone numbers of a subscriber: see [[411]].
# [[answer]] to a [[question]], minimal part of information is [[Bit#bit_.282.29|bit (2)]], which is answer [[yes]] or [[no]].
# {{countable|US|law}} A sworn statement by an authorized official filed in court briefly describing the nature of each charge against a suspect, [[tantamount]] to an [[indictment]] but without the involvement of a [[grand jury]].


